description: The Ukrainian doctor was flying on vacation when the woman went into labour.
title: Doctor steps in to deliver mid-flight baby
title_page: Doctor steps in to deliver mid-flight baby - BBC News
maintext: "The delivery was quick, and thankfully, without complications," Dr Fedchenko said. "The woman did not yell at all. I kept telling her everything would be all right, that I was a doctor and she was in safe hands."
